    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! Thanks so much for stopping by to check out my car! I\u2019ve absolutely loved driving this beauty, and it\u2019s been such a reliable companion on the road. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been well-looked after, so it\u2019s ready to hit the pavement with a new owner today. If you're looking for a smooth ride that still looks great and feels even better behind the wheel, this is the one! I\u2019d love to see it go to a good home\u2014feel free to reach out if you have any questions or want to come by for a test drive!",
