      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 30
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering a mechanically sound E92 M3 powered by the high-revving S65 4.0L naturally aspirated V8. This unit features a 6-speed manual gearbox providing direct mechanical linkage and a 3.85 final drive ratio. Performance is bolstered by the M Variable Differential Lock and Electronic Damper Control (EDC) for adjustable compression and rebound. Recent service includes documented rod bearing replacement and updated throttle actuators, ensuring the longevity of the valvetrain and rotating assembly. The chassis exhibits excellent torsional rigidity with no subframe fatigue. A purist\u2019s spec finished with the weight-saving carbon fiber roof, ready for immediate high-performance application.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
