    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Experience the precision of German engineering with this meticulously maintained 2016 Porsche Cayman. Finished in a timeless Agate Grey Metallic, the exterior retains a deep luster, though it shows minor road peppering on the front bumper consistent with spirited weekend drives. Inside, the black leather cockpit is remarkably clean, with only slight bolster wear on the driver\u2019s seat. This vehicle has been garage-kept and serviced exclusively at authorized centers, with a full folder of records to prove its mechanical health. The tires have plenty of tread remaining, and the flat-six engine note is as crisp as the day it left the showroom. It is a turn-key enthusiast car that balances daily drivability with track-ready performance. While not a museum piece, it is a shining, reliable example of a driver\u2019s car that has been loved and respected.",
      "price": 34800.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
