      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 30
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "We are pleased to present this distinguished vehicle, an exemplary choice for those seeking a harmonious blend of performance and reliability. This motorcar has been maintained to high standards, exhibiting a refined exterior and a well-appointed cabin that reflects diligent care. Engineered for consistency and longevity, it offers a sophisticated driving experience that remains as compelling today as it was at its inception. This is a premier opportunity to acquire a well-preserved asset that meets the demands of the modern road with poise and confidence.",
      "price": 34500.0,
