    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a driver\u2019s specimen featuring the legendary S54B32 naturally aspirated inline-six. The power plant pulls linearly to its 8,000 RPM redline, benefiting from recently serviced individual throttle bodies and a recalibrated double VANOS system for optimal cam timing. Power is delivered to the rear wheels via a crisp Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox and a factory M-Variable limited-slip differential. The chassis remains taut with upgraded polyurethane bushings and a reinforced subframe, mitigating common floor pan fatigue. While showing signs of honest use consistent with its age, the compression across all six cylinders remains within factory specifications, and the valve clearances have been meticulously adjusted. This is a mechanically sorted machine ready for the apex.",
